						               													<description>Blokus Shuffle: UNO Edition is a wild take on traditional Blokus.  The object of the game hasn't changed - play as many of your pieces as possible onto the board by following the one rule of Blokus: each piece you play must touch another of your pieces only at the corner.  The twist?  Each player has a deck of action cards at their disposal to really change up the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;On your turn you'll play an action card, then play your piece, then refill your hand.  The cards are UNO-themed and let you do a variety of things.  Traditional UNO standbys like Skip, Reverse, and Draw 2 are in there, but Blokus Shuffle also includes powerful new abilities like Warp, Recycle, and Edge-to-Edge.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;When no one can play anymore pieces, the game ends and the player with the fewest unplayed pieces wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
